1955;;The Shrike;;American;;José Ferrer;;José Ferrer, June Allyson;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Shrike_(film);;Successful stage director Jim Downs (Ferrer) is driven to a mental breakdown by his domineering wife Ann (June Allyson). Institutionalized, he confides in Dr. Bellman (Kendall Clark) and Dr. Barrow (Isabel Bonner), and he finds a kindred spirit in Charlotte Moore (Joy Page).